---
config:
  flowchart:
    htmlLabels: false
---
flowchart TD
  Req[Incoming consent request] --> Geo[Geo lookup MaxMind / cf-ipcountry]
  Geo --> GPC{Sec-GPC: 1?}
  GPC -->|yes| OptOut[Pre-set opt-out for sale/share categories]
  GPC -->|no| Country{ISO country code}
  OptOut --> Country
  Country -->|EU/EEA + UK| GDPR[GDPR / UK-GDPR<br>opt-in, deny by default]
  Country -->|US-CA + similar| CCPA[CCPA / CPRA<br>opt-out, allow until signal]
  Country -->|BR| LGPD[LGPD<br>opt-in, deny by default]
  Country -->|other| Default[Tenant default policy]
  GDPR --> Tenant[Tenant overrides per market]
  CCPA --> Tenant
  LGPD --> Tenant
  Default --> Tenant
  Tenant --> Decision[Effective consent policy + Google CMP signals + TCF string]
